Package: RDatastream
Type: Package
Title: A R interface for Datastream and Thomson Dataworks Enterprise
Version: 0.2
Author: Francois Cocquemas <francois.cocquemas@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Francois Cocquemas <francois.cocquemas@gmail.com>
Description: RDatastream is a R interface to the Thomson Dataworks Enterprise
    SOAP API (non free), with some convenience functions for retrieving
    Datastream data specifically. This package requires valid credentials
    for use with this API.
License: MIT
Imports:
    XML,
    RCurl,
    htmltools
Depends:
    R (>= 2.14)
Collate:
    'ds.R'
    'help.R'
    'sources.R'
